        <updateDate>2019-09-30T20:44:41Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Support Local Transportation Act</strong></p> <p>This bill revises requirements for the surface transportation block grant program to increase the percentages of program funds required to be allocated to states for each of&nbsp; FY2019-FY2020 for surface transportation projects in</p> <ul> <li>urbanized areas with a population of over 200,000, </li> <li>non-urban areas with a population greater than 5,000, and </li> <li>other areas of the state. </li></ul>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
